casebody.data:
No. 105,

Orig.

Kansas v. Colorado. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 522 U. S. 1026.]

Motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and it is ordered that the Special Master is awarded a total of $36,708.57 for the period September 10, 1997, through February 28, 1999, to be paid equally by the parties.
